| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2934 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ca038bb8-67e1-5d19-98b5-852bb41b0f18"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
